Package: nvfcapp
Version: 0.0.1-RC
Maintainer: Matt Carlotta <carlotta.matt@gmail.com>
Section: utils
Homepage: https://code.mattcarlotta.io/root/nvfcApp/
Architecture: amd64
Priority: optional
Depends: python3 (=3.6.5), libgtk-3-dev, python3-cairocffi, python3-pip, python3-matplotlib
Description: Automatically control a Nvidia GPU's fan speed
 A GTK3 (v3.18) application that creates a modifiable 2D curve of [temp, fanspeed] points that automatically controls a Nvidia GPU's fan speed according to the GPU's temp within a Linux environment.